### Auth API
@host = http://localhost:3001
@token = REPLACE_WITH_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Бүртгүүлэх (init)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "99112233",
  "name": "Тест Хэрэглэгч"
}

### Бүртгүүлэх (verify)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "99112233",
  "code": "123456"
}

### Нэвтрэх
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "99112233",
  "password": "Pass1234"
}

### Профайл өөрчлөх
PATCH {{host}}/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Шинэ нэр"
}

### Нууц үг солих
POST {{host}}/api/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "Pass1234",
  "newPassword": "NewPass5678"
}

### Идэвхтэй sessions
GET {{host}}/api/auth/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Session устгах
DELETE {{host}}/api/auth/sessions/clx_session_id
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Гарах
POST {{host}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### БҮРТГЭЛ УСТГАХ — Аюултай!
DELETE {{host}}/api/auth/account
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirm": "DELETE"
}
